original_title: 新人NO.1STYLE グラビアアイドル吉高寧々AV解禁
overview: Nene Yoshitaka made her industry debut as a gravure idol in 2017. Not only does she have a cute face, but she also has a soft and innocent personality. She was expected to play an active role in the future with unusual exposure for a newcomer such as the opening of a weekly magazine and the release of a photo book, but suddenly transferred to the AV industry! What is the reason why Gravure 1st grade fresh girl became S1 exclusive actress! ?
title: Fresh Face. No. 1 Style: The Gravure Idol. Nene Yoshitaka AV Ban.
